# Base URL for em-solar-api (no trailing slash). Used by Vite dev `runtime-config.js` and optional build-time embed.
#
# Local development: run backend with `npm run dev` in em-solar-backend, then:
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:8787
#
# --- Cloudflare Worker (this repo) — live API URL ---------------------------
# After `npm run build && wrangler deploy`, the **em-solar** Worker reads plaintext var **API_BASE_URL**
# (Settings → Variables, or `vars` in wrangler.jsonc). That value is injected via `/runtime-config.js`.
# You do NOT need VITE_API_URL on the server for production if API_BASE_URL is set on the Worker.
#
# Optional: bake URL into the static JS at build time (CI): VITE_API_URL=https://your-api.workers.dev
